title: Luxury 2 Bed, 2 Bath, 2 Garage pkg. in unit Washer/Dryer. Photos
posting_body: ['Totally beautiful unit, 2 bed, 2 bath, washer/dryer in unit', 'and 2 garage parking spaces included.', 'This sunlit unit has hardwood floors in kitchen and', 'living room, new carpet in bedrooms, and just painted.', 'Granite counters, stainless appliances, central air, walk in closet.', 'Walk out to patio and private yard.', 'No pets or smoking.', 'Located in a brick building and quick walk to Alewife Station.', 'Tenant responsible for utilities.', 'Available 8/15 or 9/1, no pets or smoking allowed.', 'Good credit and employment required.', 'Set up your viewing now.', 'Call 617-974-3019.', 'Faster connection if you call me.', 'There is a real estate fee of $3,500.', 'if you rent this unit.', 'Monaco R.E.', 'Newton, MA', '617-974-3019', 'Leave me your email address for photos.', 'Please reference: 2 Bed/2Bath Alewife in your text or message Thank you']
